{"tid":1967987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水圍夜歸女遇劫　警剝繭抽絲拉3男女","createTime":"2020-04-11T10:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:12:12.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fea59edddfb39167e0273e853333b3e20b02532","tid":1967987,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQE49iH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQE49iH.jpg&h=96f45940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方於本月8日凌晨約2時45分接獲一名女子報案，指她獨自途經天秀路一公園時，被2名男子從後襲擊並劫走其內有約3,000元財物的手袋。該2名男子其後往天晴邨方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍分區特遣隊人員經深入調查後，昨日(10日)晚上在天晴邨附近拘捕一名姓王(19歲)本地女子以及2名姓陳及姓盧(俱21歲)本地男子涉嫌行劫，並檢獲他們犯案時所穿的衣物。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，所有被捕人士現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲行劫案是十分嚴重的罪行，一經定罪，最高可判終身監禁，而近期的罪案當中，涉及青少年參與行劫案有上升趨勢。任何人特別是青少年，要珍惜前途，不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/mobile/bkn-20200411152024762-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200411152024762-0411_00822_001.html&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=dd909325\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/mobile/bkn-20200411152024762-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5a33a6e40667a9577aefc3dc853b0a64769aaa3","tid":1967987,"uid":11463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:31:11.000Z","msg":"721又唔剝？"},{"pid":"85f211f610de37dc023412a1ad7bebab8aee8d9c","tid":1967987,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"往天晴邨方向逃去<br />\n<br />\n昨日(10日)晚上在天晴邨附近拘捕一名姓王(19歲)本地女子以及2名姓陳及姓盧(俱21歲)本地男子涉嫌行劫，並檢獲他們犯案時所穿的衣物。<br />\n<br />\nON9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c42d670535413b46ca13fb85e45fee2820e213a","tid":